    <item>
      <title>埃及突破性国际货币基金组织协议将贷款额增至 80 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-gets-breakthrough-imf-deal-to-lift-loan-size-to-8-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及和国际货币基金组织同意将该国的救助计划增加一倍多，达到 80 亿美元，这是国际社会为稳定因战争和通货膨胀而资金短缺的地区关键国家所做努力的顶峰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-gets-breakthrough-imf-deal-to-lift-loan-size-to-8-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
